{"tid":1428161,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"高能鉛槍","createTime":"2019-08-07T09:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T09:23:40.000Z","uid":218778,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e7541a3219f6ec7f3b4284d07b97100375653f36","tid":1428161,"uid":218778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢一枝係一枝長30cm既鉛槍<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係硬過皮膚既紙皮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢一枝鉛槍係可以輕易插穿紙皮　 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n造成有成足足5mm大既窿 <br />\n如果插到皮膚可以造成流血(直插到眼就會引致眼球受損，嚴重會引導眼瞎)　<br />\n以往都有不少新聞及圖片表示鉛槍既威力<br />\n以下圖片包含血腥畫面<br />\n<img src=\"http://dingyue.nosdn.127.net/GRnU5gy4mUFyaB48Cd9vAaC1H6ki8k2SuL8pBKZhwT0Y41523505748081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.nosdn.127.net%2FGRnU5gy4mUFyaB48Cd9vAaC1H6ki8k2SuL8pBKZhwT0Y41523505748081.jpg&h=8aa4c0d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://13n.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/715452-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F13n.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F715452-1.jpg&h=29433293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n椅豎鉛筆插同學陰道 中五生認傷人︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20150409/s00002/1428516154696\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20150409%2Fs00002%2F1428516154696&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQwPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=263ea8bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20150409%2Fs00002%2F1428516154696&h=33a79f37\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20150409/s00002/1428516154696</a><br />\n【恐怖意外】加女童學校跌倒鉛筆插頸 但手術後兩日已可出院<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190518&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59609898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190518%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59609898&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQwPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=b5ea5af4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190518%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59609898&h=00855f44\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190518&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59609898</a><br />\n而根據香港條例第217章 《武器條例》附表[第2及17條]<br />\n違禁武器包括<br />\n中國式飛鏢<br />\n重力刀<br />\n重力操作鋼棒<br />\n指節套，不論是否有尖釘及是否有刀刃<br />\n附有手柄的鐵鏈<br />\n彈簧鋼棒<br />\n任何以彈簧或其他機械或電動裝置露出刀刃的刀  <br />\n(由1990年第394號法律公告增補)<br />\n任何有刀刃或尖端的武器，其設計是在使用時以拳頭緊握手柄，而刀刃或尖端則從拳頭指縫間突出  <br />\n(由1990年第394號法律公告增補)<br />\n(由1990年第394號法律公告修訂)<br />\n<br />\n呢枝鉛槍係符合任何有刀刃或尖端的武器，其設計是在使用時以拳頭緊握手柄，而刀刃或尖端則從拳頭指縫間突出呢項條件<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yL08nBp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyL08nBp.jpg&h=232ac202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以請各位要小心，盡量避免攜帶出外<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407b7b01fcd97fb03aa61bde881e3fa6266b8a20","tid":1428161,"uid":261582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:03:09.000Z","msg":"恭喜你<br />\n歡迎加入警隊<br />\n你最快幾時可以返工"},{"pid":"a2869a408967b9236f9524e7ff488efb0c3d1e43","tid":1428161,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551b8e7b1a2cdfd9b5243048a53565585d5e55b1","tid":1428161,"uid":34705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:23:40.000Z","msg":"大殺傷力武器啦直頭"}]}